Class GreaterThanOrEqualToConditionalSearchCriteria

java.lang.Object
com.samupert.univpm.eurostat.filtering.criteria.conditional.ConditionalSearchCriteria<Number>
com.samupert.univpm.eurostat.filtering.criteria.conditional.GreaterThanOrEqualToConditionalSearchCriteria
All Implemented Interfaces:
SearchCriteriaSpecification, Serializable, org.springframework.data.jpa.domain.Specification<MonetaryPoverty>
public class GreaterThanOrEqualToConditionalSearchCriteria extends ConditionalSearchCriteria<Number>
The conditional search criteria specification that checks if the field value is greater or equal to the given value. See Specification.
The JSON filter is: 
 {
     "operation": "$gte",
     "fieldName": "timePeriod",
     "value": 2017
  }
